Count Odd or Even

Write a program to count the number of even and odd elements in an array:

Sample Input:
3
1
2
3

Sample Output:
Odd: 2
Even: 1

Code :

import java.util.*;
public class Count
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int n=sc.nextInt();
        int arr[]=new int[n];;
        int i,Odd =0,Even = 0;
        for ( i = 0; i <n; i++) 
        {
            arr[i] =sc.nextInt();
            if(arr[i]%2== 1)
            {
              Odd =Odd + 1;
            }
            else
            {
                Even = Even + 1;
            }
        }
        System.out.println("Odd: "+Odd);
        System.out.println("Even: "+Even);

    }
}
